OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with a few light
OL,6,Fshowers, brighter conditions reaching
OL,7,FShetland by mid morning and cloud
OL,8,Fbreaking for Orkney soon after. Dry
OL,9,Fand bright with sunny spells during
OL,10,Fthe afternoon, feeling cooler despite
OL,11,Flight winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry with some evening
OL,14,Fsunshine, turning cloudier at times
OL,15,Fduring the night and a gentle
OL,16,Fnortherly wind building, perhaps some
OL,17,Fpatchy rain reaching Orkney by dawn.
OL,18,FQuite a cool night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
