OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA bright start for Shetland
OL,6,Fbut cloudier with some light rain at
OL,7,Ffirst for Orkney. turning into a wet
OL,8,Fafternoon with showery rain.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA
OL,11,Fcloudy and damp start to the the new
OL,12,Fweek but conditions improving on
OL,13,FMonday. Light winds and a mix of cloud
OL,14,Fand brighter spells continuing towards
OL,15,Fmid week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
